      "Ingredients": "- 1 1/2 loaves French bread\n- 8 eggs, beaten\n- 1 cup milk\n- 1 cup half and half\n- 2 T sugar\n- 1/4 tsp cinnamon\n- 1/4 tsp nutmeg\n- 1 T vanilla\n\nTopping\n- 1 cup brown sugar\n- 2 T light corn syrup\n- 1/2 tsp nutmeg\n- 1/2 tsp cinnamon\n- 1/2 lb butter softened\n- 1 cup chopped pecans",
