      "Description": "The most amazing potato salad ever. Seriously.",
      "Ingredients": "- 5lb bag potatoes\n- 8 boiled eggs\n- 4 T Parsley flakes \n- 1 cup chopped onion \n\nDressing\n- 2/3 cups vinegar\n- 1/2 cup oil\n- 4 T sugar\n- 2 tsp salt\n- 1/2 tsp pepper",
