      "Description": "Homemade guacamole. This is so much better than the store bought stuff because you can taste the freshness and just tastes better in general.",
      "Ingredients": "- 2 ripe avocadoes\n- ½ cup chopped onion\n- ¼ cup chopped green chilies  (you can buy the canned chilies to speed up the process)\n- 1 T lime juice (use more or less based on your preference) \n- ½ tsp salt\n- Dash of pepper \n- ½ chopped firm tomato or use about ¼ cup salsa (How much you use depends on personal preference)",
