      "Description": "We all know what nachos are",
      "Ingredients": "- 1 pound ground beef                                                                           \n- Tortilla Chips\n- 1 package of taco seasoning (If using your own seasonings use 2t chili powder, ½ t salt, ½ garlic powder, dash of pepper, ½ t cumin, 1/4t oregano.  Then taste it and see if you want more of a spice.  Then add ¼ c of water mix and let thicken.)\n- 1 small chopped onion (depends on how big your nacho is, how much you need)\n- Chopped lettuce\n- Chopped tomato\n- Sour cream\n- Salsa\n- Jalapeños (optional)\n- Pepper rings (optional)\n- Guacamole (optional) You can buy it or make it.\n- Shredded mozzerella cheese",
