      "Ingredients": "- 1¼ cups boiling water\n- 1 cup quick oats\n- ½ cup butter\n- 1 cup white sugar\n- 1 cup brown sugar\n- 2 eggs, beaten\n- 1 tsp cinnamon\n- 1 tsp baking soda\n- 1⅓ cups flour\n\nFrosting\n- 6 T butter\n- ½ cup brown sugar\n- ¼ cup cream",
