      "Name": "Raw Apple Cake",
      "Description": "A recipe from Grammy (Sara Satterlee)",
      "Ingredients": "- 1½ cup oil\n- 1½ cup sugar\n- 2 eggs\n- 3 cups flour\n- 1 tsp soda\n- 1 tsp salt\n- 1 tsp cinnamon\n- 2 tsp vanilla\n- ½ cup chopped nuts\n- ½ cup shredded coconut\n- 3 cups raw apple, diced thin",
      "Instructions": "- Mix oil, sugar and eggs together in one bowl\n- In a larger bowl sift together flour, salt, soda and cinnamon\n- Add eggs mixture to flour mixture\n- Mix well\n- Add the rest of the ingredients\n- Mix well\n- Pour into greased and floured 13 x 9 pan\n- Bake at 350* for 35 minutes\n- Top with powdered sugar when it comes out of the oven",
